OpenHAB - client setup
======================
1. As root run the following command for generating the proxy user
	htpasswd -c /etc/nginx/.htpasswd opnhbProxy

2. Take note of the openVPN IP (see tun0 interface), it should be 10.8.0.1

3. Install Openhab client

4. Access openVPN

5. Open OpenHAB client then:
     - Settings > Connection > Remote
     - Server: https://10.8.0.1:8443
     - Username and password: use credentials generated at point 1
